  <!--
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    ADDICTION ARC STAGE DEFS
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    Fixed-sequence stages for each addiction arc. Each uses grammarRoleOverride
    so the resolver finds addiction_{substance}_{stage}_{title/body} keys.
    Six stages per substance: opening, dependency, social, withdrawal, crisis, choice.
    "choice" is the climax stage - presents hard road (sobriety) vs easy out.
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  -->

